PJs Coffee being right next to our hotel, the French Market Inn, was perfect for helping caffeinate and feed us the morning of my husband and I’s wedding. PJs actually has a connecting door to the hotel! We got married early Feb 2020 before the pandemic hit the U.S. We spoke with the manager a couple of days before the wedding about providing an assortment of sweet and savory, warm and cold baked goods for food as well as a few big containers of coffee. The manager went above and beyond by ensuring that she and one of her employees could come in extra early that day to fulfill our request. The food was very tasty, the coffee was great – and they provided everything we needed for the coffee, cups, cream, sugar, napkins – you name it, we got it! Our guests and bridal party were well fed and energized for our big day! We ended up buying bags of coffee and k-cups (especially Southern Wedding Cake flavor) to take back home with us to NC, and now we get PJs delivered to our home. Great experience, great coffee.
